=Episode 4=

11
00:00:45,140 --> 00:00:50,660
(I Am Waiting for
the Wedding Ring from You)

12
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,280
Yinchuan, are you in there?

13
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,350
How could you come in?

14
00:01:15,150 --> 00:01:17,280
I called you from outside,
but you didn't respond,

15
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,430
so I came in.

16
00:01:18,510 --> 00:01:20,120
Don't come over. I am naked.

17
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,760
I want to borrow some money from you.

18
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,430
I don't want to talk to my father.

19
00:01:25,590 --> 00:01:26,040
No problem.

20
00:01:26,950 --> 00:01:28,200
I will send the servant
to take it to you later.

21
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,430
You are really nice to me, Yichuan.

22
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:31,230
I also want...

23
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,640
Let's talk about it tomorrow.

24
00:01:32,790 --> 00:01:33,480
I am kind of tired.

25
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:11,520
Thank you.

26
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,360
So, Lu Xiaoqian fancies you?

27
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:29,030
Are you jealous?

28
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:33,190
How about you?

29
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,360
Do you fancy her?

30
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,750
Two years ago,

31
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,000
I found the woman I love the most.

32
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,780
♪Fallen flowers figured autumn out♪

33
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:54,980
♪They bid farewell in the moonlight♪

34
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:57,660
♪It's like our fate♪

35
00:02:57,660 --> 00:03:02,940
♪After we parted,
our love turned to dust♪

36
00:03:03,380 --> 00:03:06,780
♪Away faded our indelible feelings♪

37
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:10,260
♪Going through
the unavoidable ups and downs♪

38
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:14,300
♪I try to forget
with the change of seasons♪

39
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:17,860
♪But I can't erase you from my mind♪

40
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:21,460
♪I miss you like the wind
rises among the branches♪

41
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:25,620
♪It sweeps through my heart,
causing ripples♪

42
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:29,980
♪Reminiscing about the past in tears,
I dare not expect♪

43
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:33,380
♪You will detect this secret♪

44
00:03:35,590 --> 00:03:36,190
Master.

45
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,400
Where is Yichuan?

46
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:40,240
He is resting in his room.

47
00:03:41,100 --> 00:03:43,820
♪The sight of you took my breath away♪

48
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,750
The Lu's house
is a dangerous place.

49
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:54,080
Lu Ding is not a simple person.

50
